Title: Army recruitment rally on Sept. 4
Content: A recruitment rally of 118 Infantry battalion (Territorial Army) Grenadiers will be held from Sept. 4 to 10 at Fort Sitabuldi, Nagpur for personnel belonging to Andhra Pradesh, Telangana, Gujarat, Ker
